{"tid":1980532,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] 牧場物語：重聚礦石鎮 #12","createTime":"2020-04-20T06:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T10:30:14.000Z","uid":82879,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"95769eb4e26446e53e5b085de56d14bba7324e50","tid":1980532,"uid":82879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://asia.sega.com/bokumono/cht/img/top/keyvisual.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fasia.sega.com%2Fbokumono%2Fcht%2Fimg%2Ftop%2Fkeyvisual.png&h=24d9caf4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>請盡量用不推文回覆</strong></span></div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awZjibO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawZjibO.jpg&h=48068a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxH8VYu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxH8VYu.jpg&h=46f243c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSrtVYv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSrtVYv.jpg&h=6cb13fa0&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Q&amp;A</span></span></ins><br />\n1. 邊度拎魚竿？  身上留空位去海邊小屋<br />\n2. 點放低木石資材？ 家中左上櫃<br />\n3. 斧頭之類點拎？ 家中右下角櫃<br />\n4. 一開始點賺錢？ 種蘿蔔先啦，之後賽馬賺第一桶金，儲錢夏天種菠蘿<br />\n5. 詛咒工具使唔使全秘銀先刷到？ 唔使，有巴打全1lv工具都刷到<br />\n6. 牧草究竟係點種？ 擺一舊喺未耕過嘅田度，四周圍有位無嘢阻住佢就會自己繼續生，但係唔好一開始就放牛出去食，食哂全部就唔會繼續生<br />\n7. 基本操作唔識就去睇書架新手教學<br />\n[/b]<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">賭馬攻略</span></span></ins><br />\n首先大家計下自己需要幾多馬票：<br />\n如果你得細袋（Total 16格），假設你想填滿哂個袋，你會最少需要16 x 9 x 18  = 2592張票<br />\n如果你有大袋（Total 24格），最少需要24 x 9 x 18  = 3888張票<br />\n如果你仲想買其他野，例如力之果實，你就自己加需要既票數落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一張馬票50蚊，如果你有5000蚊，你就會買到100張<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後將你需要既票數除返你買到嘅票數就係你需要S/L到嘅賠率<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假設你要2592張馬票，你有5000蚊，你所需要既賠率就係2592/(5000/50) = 25.92，換然之你就要26倍嘅賠率啲馬票先夠你用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">S/L方法</span></span></ins><br />\nS/L方法嘅概念係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Load出一個滿意嘅賠率表</span></span>，而<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係一味剩係Load同一場馬Load到贏</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我見有啲人Load左幾粒鐘都贏唔到，係因為你係同緊人地隻一倍兩倍大熱鬥啊，Load到瞓著都未贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地嘅目標係Load到一個好既賠率表，就好似呢張咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzrejpN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzrejpN.jpg&h=3d977b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隻隻馬都係十幾倍個贏既機率咪高好多囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點係，S/L賠率表快過你就咁S/L同一場馬好多次<br />\n<br />\n我地既目標係要Load到一個齊集以下兩個條件既賠率表，咁你贏既機會就會高好多：<br />\n1：每隻馬最低賠率全部大過15<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（大約咁上下啦）</span><br />\n2：最少有一隻馬嘅賠率 &gt;= 你要既賠率<br />\n<br />\n當你Load到呢個賠率表之後，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">應該</span>不出三五次你就會贏到<br />\n<br />\n<ins>S/L方法我建議有兩種：</ins><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">方法一：</span></ins><br />\n1. 18號10點喺廣場入口前Save<br />\n2. 入去第一場賠率唔需要理會（因為固定左）<br />\n3. 第二場如果賠率表滿意就All in（跳到5），唔滿意就唔落Bet<br />\n4. 第三場如果見到有你需要既賠率就All in，橫掂係最後一場<br />\n5. 如果贏就恭喜你，輸就行出場地，返到房就Load返個Save，跳到1<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">方法二（交緊青瓜嘅你，呢個方法會好辛苦）：</span></ins><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">16號</span></span>臨瞓前Save（Save 1）<br />\n2. 如果唔洗交青瓜／做其他緊要野，17號起身直接瞓返落床<br />\n2.5. 如果要交青瓜／做其他野就做完返去瞓<br />\n3. 18號10點喺廣場入口前Save（Save 2）<br />\n4. 第一場如果賠率表滿意就跳到5，如果唔係就熄Game，Load Save 1<br />\n5. 如果贏就恭喜你，輸就熄Game，Load Save 2（跳去4）<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">寵物入手方法</span></span></ins><br />\n1. 扔30日野落女神個湖到<br />\n2.然後星期3（一定要好天）朝早出門口就會有個肥佬黎搵你。每個星期3都會在宿屋妹小蘭樓上最埋面間房到擺檔賣野。<br />\n3. 每個月15號PM12:30-05:50在廣場擺檔賣寵物<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更新檔重點內容</span></span></ins><br />\n<del>廢青</del>克里夫如果走咗都可以返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(第2年起任意月份嘅29日下午6-10由鍛造店隔離條路行上去莊園觸發劇情)<br />\n供奉女神累計100日可以解鎖礦場電梯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家要將全部道具升級做秘銀先可以挖到詛咒道具<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n電視搖控賣價少咗個0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>有用攻略(巴哈姆特)</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">【心得】《牧場物語︰重聚礦石鎮》不專業攻略整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D1405%26snA%3D24821&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=bef4537c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24821</a><br />\n【心得】礦石鎮 年間行事曆 隱藏活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D1405%26snA%3D24779&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=1a1c1973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24779</a><br />\n【心得】【重聚礦石鎮】關於交往戀人事件到結婚的介紹＆統整<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D1405%26snA%3D24820&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=31ac7c6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24820</a><br />\n【攻略】【重聚礦石鎮】戀愛對象完整事件攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D1405%26snA%3D24966&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=13f70c13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=24966</a><br />\n【情報】【更新資料】《牧場物語：重聚礦石鎮》日文版Ver.1.1.2/亞洲版Ver.1.1.1 今天開始配信！<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=25226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D1405%26snA%3D25226&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=651c0c30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=1405&amp;snA=25226</a></span>"},{"pid":"425a5f91cac98ea800a7fddca1406ad29fa83d62","tid":1980532,"uid":82879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"雖然推得好慢但見1001咗所以幫手開過個<br />\n順便補少少更新內容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過呢排個個都動森架啦</span>"},{"pid":"09e476869542a3b2214a8d96e79830e120c87a78","tid":1980532,"uid":72142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"425a5f91cac98ea800a7fddca1406ad29fa83d62","tid":1980532,"uid":82879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:00:23.000Z","msg":"雖然推得好慢但見1001咗所以幫手開過個<br />\n順便補少少更新內容<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">不過呢排個個都動森架啦</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T07:04:51.000Z","msg":"動森係進階版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282d4038cdb0a5014750b6fa11504e465cc8728e","tid":1980532,"uid":82879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09e476869542a3b2214a8d96e79830e120c87a78","tid":1980532,"uid":72142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"425a5f91cac98ea800a7fddca1406ad29fa83d62","tid":1980532,"uid":82879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0